                                                  <h2>Australian Multiculturalism</h2>
                                                  <p>Australia is a country with a successful democracy, a wealth in natural resources, and a diversity of people. <br />It has known over the time the development of a multicultural society. <br />(The Parliament of the Commonwealth of Australia, 2011)</p>  
                                        </div>
